unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection on the United Federation of Teachers
abstract_ssm: The United Federation of Teachers (American Federation of Teachers, Local 2) represents public school teachers and associated personnel in New York City.  This collection contains a wide variety of printed ephemera such as constitutions, agreements, brochures, clippings, flyers, pamphlets, reports and other items reflecting the history and activities of the union.
